@NODE PD
@TITLE "PD Company"


PD Company:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Thankyou for stocking ProTitler in your collection.  If you haven't already
read the @{" distribution "link Unregistered} details, please do so now.

Remember you may only stock the UNREGISTERED version.

@ENDNODE


@NODE MiscMenu
@TITLE "Misc Menu"



Misc Menu
~~~~~~~~~~~


This contains everything else I didn't include anywhere else :)



